Title: Happiness project
DateModified: '2018-02-28'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/happiness-project
SetInCountry: India
Category: A decision that pushed me to the edge
AuthorName: Ahalya  V S
AuthorCountry: India
Text: The story begins in the small state of India where a big little girl with matured
  age lying on a bed thinking about how her life just passed through all these years.
  She have a miserable past while she used to think about it a narrow smile ending
  with a deep confusion interrogating herself why God has given her this life but
  she always had a dream which lead her towards the future what she have dreamed years
  before . Such a humble dream that she wants to live happy all day but she knew that
  no humans have ever lived happy everyday . She loved to travel and was an artist
  who always imprint the scenes that flashes in front of her . Simple scenery gave
  her extreme happiness such as mother cow lactating . She loved all the different
  faces around her . So she decided that she will start loving the people around .
  She started spreading the smile wherever she roam around . She started forgetting
  about her past . A pencil and a paper let her bring joy towards the positive life
  . She never believed in a marraige since she belonged to a broken family . She started
  talking to the blooming flowers , she started to bring the light to wipe out the
  darkness which she was always feared of . Finally she achieved that goal " The happiness
  project ". She started writing stories with people around her . She was happy at
  the end of day .
